Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Keyable, PersonInterface

    public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
implements PersonInterface
    This class represents a person to be stored in an address book utility It contains the persons first and last names, phone number and address Provides methods to sort the person in a hash table
    Author:
    Adam Holt
